<h3>The Cost Per Lead Problem</h3>
<p>The average HVAC lead from Google Ads costs <a href="https://www.schulzecreativellc.com/blog/2026-google-ads-statistics-for-hvac-businesses">$104</a>. Premium keywords like "emergency AC repair near me" cost $25+ per click. At a 10% conversion rate, that is $250 per lead from paid search alone.</p>
<p>Social media generates leads at a fraction of that cost. Facebook group engagement and organic posts generate leads for free. Facebook Ads for HVAC companies run $10 to $20 per day and generate 5 to 15 leads per month. Compare that to $3,000+/month for competitive Google Ads campaigns.</p>
<h3>Social Media Builds What Ads Cannot</h3>
<p>Paid ads stop the moment you stop paying. Social media content compounds. A before-and-after video of a furnace installation posted today drives views for months. A customer testimonial shared today builds trust with every person who visits your profile for the next year.</p>
<p>The HVAC companies winning on social media are not spending more. They are showing up consistently. That consistency makes them the default choice in their service area.</p>
